[0016]    The present disclosure is explained in more detail on the basis of the drawings, in which
Figure 1  schematically shows the overall view of a separating device as disclosed herein;
Figure 2  shows a cross-sectional view of a separating device as disclosed herein;
Figures 3A - 3L  show various details of the stack of annular discs of a separating device as disclosed herein;
Figures 4A - 4L  show various details of the stack of annular discs of a separating device as disclosed herein;
Figures 5A - 5B  show different views of a perforated pipe and a band which is provided helically in axial direction on the outer surface of the perforated pipe of a separating device as disclosed herein; and
Figures 6A - 6B  show different views of a perforated pipe and a band which is provided helically in axial direction on the outer surface of the perforated pipe of a separating device as disclosed herein.
